    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>向树海之巅进发！</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《雾隐天途》是一款以参天巨树枝干为背景的垂直城市建造游戏。你将管理稀有的光源与火焰，守护被绿荫环抱的家园，抵御逐步逼近、吞噬一切的迷雾侵袭。采集资源、研发技术、调配人力，并派出坚定的先锋队深入先民遗迹，揭开他们的秘密与文明覆灭的真相。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> </i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个交织着民间恐怖传说与诡异生物的世界里，游戏将城市建造、塔防策略与探索冒险巧妙融合，带来一场别具一格的沉浸式体验。穿行于瑰丽而危险的环境中，欣赏电影级的过场动画，沉浸在由《雾隐天途》系列作曲家<strong>山冈晃</strong>亲自打造的氛围音乐中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/a4587175906d7b160392f450da398f5e.poster.avif?t=1772201493\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/a4587175906d7b160392f450da398f5e.webm?t=1772201493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/a4587175906d7b160392f450da398f5e.mp4?t=1772201493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >依托巨树的枝干向上拓展你的居所。在有限的横向空间中精巧布局，建设滑索、升降梯和阶梯，将不断扩张的领地互相连接。你需要高效管理资源、生产设备与居民士气，同时强化防御，迎战迷雾带来的混乱与灾厄。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/313ffc50adadb658e67983eed5f357c8.poster.avif?t=1772201493\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/313ffc50adadb658e67983eed5f357c8.webm?t=1772201493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/313ffc50adadb658e67983eed5f357c8.mp4?t=1772201493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迷雾冷酷无情，它令居民陷入疯狂，制造恐惧与混乱。你必须照亮前路，研发光能武器，掌控被称为“索利姆”的原始能量，击退侵蚀的阴霾。在危机中作出道德抉择，考验你的领导力，激励居民在未知威胁下保持希望与坚韧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/67f4c04a37c9eff285208d5e571184eb.poster.avif?t=1772201493\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/67f4c04a37c9eff285208d5e571184eb.webm?t=1772201493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/67f4c04a37c9eff285208d5e571184eb.mp4?t=1772201493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >派遣侦察小队前往迷雾笼罩的未知区域，绘制航线、建立前哨、开采珍稀资源。你将遭遇潜伏于暗影中的异形生物，发现前文明留下的遗迹与禁忌科技。发掘失落的文物与被遗忘的知识，拼凑这个世界破碎的过往。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/7b46614e9c6cb76ba4afad122fa5e97a.poster.avif?t=1772201493\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/7b46614e9c6cb76ba4afad122fa5e97a.webm?t=1772201493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/7b46614e9c6cb76ba4afad122fa5e97a.mp4?t=1772201493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在复杂的多线故事中体验道德考验。四位主人公，各怀信念与秘密，将带来截然不同的视角与命运交织。你的每一个选择都可能带来深远后果，哪怕只是微小的举动，也可能改变一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132870/extras/5588af7afdaad494088f71128a729f14.avif?t=1772201493\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔍 游戏亮点</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>两种游戏模式</strong>：剧情模式（包含任务、支线与关键抉择） &amp; 自由模式（专注建造与探索）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超20小时单人游戏体验</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>80+ 种独特建筑</strong>：打造个性化树城</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>11类资源系统</strong>：合理分配原材料与加工品，维持城市运转</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4大技术阶段</strong>：逐步解锁新技术与建筑</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>200米垂直巨树</strong>：你的城市根植于其之上</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>40分钟氛围原声音乐</strong>：由《寂静岭》系列作曲家<strong>山冈晃</strong>倾力创作</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
